Document any aliases or shell helpers you rely on so agents reproduce your workflow.

* `uvp` → `uv run` (alias)
* `uvpo` → `uv run poe` (poe-the-poet alias)
* … *(soju-specific: e.g. `docker compose --profile ollama up ollama ollama-pull web` to start web + local AI)*

